{"tid":1866754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"排隊買口罩既老人家不乏屌鳩後生仔既廢老","createTime":"2020-02-07T01:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T12:44:55.000Z","uid":2559,"like":435,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"c30c63d0c3adbb1ff010889a641e06f84be919e0","tid":1866754,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:11:39.000Z","msg":"超過半年前，全港有一百萬人二百萬人行足十個鐘，只係為左爭取政府聽取訴求。<br />\n<br />\n呢半年黎，唔少人係警署門口苦等四十八小時，只係為左見返佢地親人。<br />\n<br />\n呢一個月以黎一大班老人家凌晨開始排隊，為左買到一盒屬於佢地既口罩。<br />\n<br />\n當中不乏當日對住三色台屌鳩後生仔既廢老藍絲，平時離地就屌柒人，到真係自己瀨野要用到自己既時間同資源時就出黎為自己發聲屌柒政府不理市民死活。<br />\n<br />\n兩蚊搭車，不敢說政府半點不好，每日周圍散播愚昧，呢啲廢老唔洗通宵達旦風吹雨打排果幾個鐘頭就嗌生嗌死，自私到咁既人係無資格要求得到其他人既尊敬同可憐。"},{"pid":"9a8f62eb9361cef19efe36555ae8b29166892913","tid":1866754,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:14:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc98eb69d2fe9fae53338272e4bbedcd52b25a78","tid":1866754,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1a505681384e444e2c32b00c2e49ccd58401e2","tid":1866754,"uid":2559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b74e14444cc72d96cd884ee9398ccd372cf9376","tid":1866754,"uid":14671,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"所以每次睇新聞見到廢老排都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a35ec80bd7f969f65af76ad80f5a37e20992f2c","tid":1866754,"uid":2559,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"7b74e14444cc72d96cd884ee9398ccd372cf9376","tid":1866754,"uid":14671,"like":87,"dislike":3,"score":84,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"所以每次睇新聞見到廢老排都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/